---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Notary Public Kiribati - Ms. Tekarei Tautua | Certified Notarial Services"
  description="Ms. Tekarei Tautua, duly appointed Notary Public of the Republic of Kiribati. Professional certification and authentication of legal documents for domestic and international use."
  lang="en"
>
  <Fragment slot="logo">Notary Tautua</Fragment>
  <Fragment slot="footer-name">Tekarei Tautua – Notary Public, Republic of Kiribati</Fragment>

  <section class="hero">
    <h1>Notary Public</h1>
    <p class="notary-name">Ms. Tekarei Tautua</p>
    <p>Providing professional notarial services with integrity, precision, and full respect for legal standards. Duly appointed Notary Public of the Republic of Kiribati, supporting the certification and authentication of legal documents for domestic and international use.</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Document Certification</h2>
      <p>Official certification of legal documents including affidavits, statutory declarations, powers of attorney, and sworn statements for use in Kiribati and abroad.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>International Authentication</h2>
      <p>Authentication and legalization of documents for international use. Supporting individuals, businesses, and government agencies with cross-border documentation needs.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Witnessing & Attestation</h2>
      <p>Professional witnessing of signatures, oaths, and affirmations. Each attestation performed with strict adherence to applicable legal requirements.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Certified Copies</h2>
      <p>Preparation and certification of true copies of original documents for legal, immigration, and administrative purposes.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Business & Commercial Services</h2>
      <p>Notarial services for corporate documents, contracts, partnership agreements, and commercial transactions requiring official authentication.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h2>Confidentiality & Integrity</h2>
      <p>Each service is delivered with strict confidentiality, accuracy, and adherence to applicable legal requirements of the Republic of Kiribati.</p>
    </article>
  </div>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>

  <section class="contact-info">
    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p><strong>Tekarei Tautua</strong> – Notary Public</p>
    <p>Betio, South Tarawa</p>
    <p>P.O. Box 118</p>
    <p>Republic of Kiribati</p>
  </section>

  <div class="ad-slot">Ad Space - Google AdSense</div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .notary-name {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    opacity: 1;
  }
  .contact-info {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 32px;
    margin-top: 32px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .contact-info h2 {
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    color: #1a1a2e;
  }
  .contact-info p {
    margin: 4px 0;
    color: #555;
  }
</style>
